==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sightly
<hw>Sight"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Pleasing
to the sight; comely.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Many brave, <xex>sightly</xex>
horses.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>L'Estrange.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Open to sight; conspicuous; <as>as, a house stands
in a <ex>sightly</ex> place</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sightproof</ent>⟦br⟧
